實係睇唔慣姐 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1d87f99b13ba045d3ddbdeaa13f56a371025f3e","tid":453962,"uid":61443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T09:19:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>電影行 24格 <br />\n聽講係因為24格<br />\n最接近人眼望到既嘢 <br />\n<br />\n聽返黎㗎咋 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好似係話人眼最多接受到每秒24格 <br />\n所以會睇落比較cinematic feel</blockquote><br />\n人眼唔止24格<br />\n只係24格啱啱好令人感覺到係連續影像<br />\n同埋拍戲用菲林係好燒錢<br />\n所以平衡影像質素同資源下就決定用24fps做標準</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n打機好似行 fps 60 ?</blockquote><br />\n應該唔只？ 唔係好識打機點計法<br />\n隻mon有唔同Hz<br />\n唔同game 唔同hardware 會有唔同fps</blockquote><br />\n打機係dynamic + cap<br />\n你個Mon set 60hz 就係cap<br />\ndisplay 唔update 個Mon 就照show 舊果張<br />\n所以你打機可以因為display 慢而得30fps , to 但個Mon 就行緊60hz<br />\n因為你張display 其實每1／30一秒先update 一次個Mon</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好多高手 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過呢到普通人有啲唔明 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4668da142743cf456866eb1aaa2b004eb8fbf6d0","tid":453962,"uid":61443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T17:11:19.000Z","msg":"點解而家叫 4k <br />\n唔叫 2160 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c64b9251268b04ca930db4ecda3569141d638329","tid":453962,"uid":12443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T18:02:13.000Z","msg":"有研究者留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20b7bb019feec346b73ebfe5c2fd4e0109dce477","tid":453962,"uid":12443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T18:04:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解而家叫 4k <br /